    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The process of joining two or more molecules of the same kind to form a more complex molecule with different physical properties.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
